            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d90717-Hd1e108">Rubrica 6</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d90717-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De mutua dilectione et fide mariti ex vxoris</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d90717-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="83"/>¶ De mutua dilectione et fide mariti et
      <lb ed="#V" n="84"/>vxoris. ¶ Rubrica. 6.
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d90717-d1e121">
               <lb ed="#V" n="85"/> <ref>IN genesit. 2 c.</ref> Relique:
      <lb ed="#V" n="86"/>homo patrem
      <lb ed="#V" n="87"/>et matrem et adherebit vxori sue: et
      <lb ed="#V" n="88"/>erunt duo in carne vna. 
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d90717-d1e132">
               <lb ed="#V" n="89"/>
         <ref>¶ Aristotelis ethincorum. l. 8. c. 7.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d90717-Qd1e136">Uiro et vxori
        <lb ed="#V" n="90"/>amicitia videtur secundum naumam existere. homo enim <!--269.xml-->
        <pb ed="#V" n="115-v"/>
                  <cb ed="#V" n="a"/>
                  <lb ed="#V" n="1"/>in nam coniugale magis quam polyticum. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d90717-d1e151"> 
            <ref>/ Idem
        <lb ed="#V" n="2"/>hyconomicorum vel. i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d90717-Qd1e153">Communicatio femine et
        <lb ed="#V" n="3"/>masculi nam est maxime. Maximus est ho
        <lb ed="#V" n="4" break="no"/>nor. honeste mulieri si respicit virum suum
        <lb ed="#V" n="5"/>castum esse in eam: et de nulla alia muliere cu
        <lb ed="#V" n="6" break="no"/>rare: sed preter omnes alias propriam et ami
        <lb ed="#V" n="7"/>cam et fidelem putet eam. Si mulier cogno
        <lb ed="#V" n="8"/>uerit fideliter et iuste virum erga se fore: et
        <lb ed="#V" n="9"/>ipsa iuste et fideliter erga virum suum erit.
        <lb ed="#V" n="10"/>Nihil est proprius nec maius vxori: precio
        <lb ed="#V" n="11"/>sa communicatione et fideli ad virum.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d90717-d1e178">
               <lb ed="#V" n="12"/>
       <ref>¶ Paulus apostolus: in epstola ad ephesios. c.
        <lb ed="#V" n="13"/>5.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d90717-Qd1e182">Ita viri debent diligere vxores suas vt
        <lb ed="#V" n="14"/>corpora sua. Qui suam vxorem diligit seip
        <lb ed="#V" n="15"/>sum diligit. Unusquisque suam vxorem sicut
        <lb ed="#V" n="16"/>semetipsum diligat. Uxor autem timeat vi
        <lb ed="#V" n="17"/>rum.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d90717-d1e196"> 
          <ref>/ Idem epistola ad collossenses. c. 3. et pe.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="18"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d90717-Qd1e198">Uiri diligite vxores vestras: et nolite ama
        <lb ed="#V" n="19" break="no"/>ri esse ad alias.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d90717-d1e206">
               <lb ed="#V" n="20"/>
         <ref>/ Seneca tragediarum in agamenone. c. 4.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="21"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d90717-Qd1e210">Ultimum est malum:
        <lb ed="#V" n="22"/>Palam mariti possidens pelex domum.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d90717-d1e218">
               <lb ed="#V" n="23"/>
       <ref>/ In hercule etheo. c. 5.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="24"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d90717-Qd1e222">O quam cruentus feminam stimulat dolor:
        <lb ed="#V" n="25"/>Cum patuit vna pelici et nupte domus.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d90717-d1e230">
               <lb ed="#V" n="26"/>
          <ref>¶ Lucanus. vel. 8.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d90717-Qd1e234">Ultima debet
        <lb ed="#V" n="27"/>Esse fides lugere virum.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d90717-d1e241">
               <lb ed="#V" n="28"/>
            <ref>¶ Cato: capitulo i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d90717-Qd1e245">Coniugem ama.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d90717-d1e249">
               <lb ed="#V" n="29"/>
          <ref>/ Capitulo. 4</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="30"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d90717-Qd1e253">Uxoris linguam si frugi est ferre memento. </quote>
            </p>
